window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A clue he can't refuse. A murder he can't remember.... </p> <p>Join thousands of fans around the world who can't get enough of <i>USA Today</i> best-selling author Mark Dawson's John Milton thrillers! </p> <p>John Milton's life is about to change. The former government assassin follows a lead to Manila that he hopes will transform everything. But things don't go to plan. He never expected to wake up in an unfamiliar hotel room beside a dead body. And, unfortunately for him, Milton doesn't remember a thing about the night before.... </p> <p>Thrown into a gruesome Filipino prison, he puts together the clues of his betrayal. With no allies and even less hope, Milton must use his wits to escape and take revenge on the men who put him there. If he doesn't lose his life in the process.... </p> <p><i>Blackout</i> is the tenth book in Mark Dawson's gripping series of John Milton thrillers. If you like gripping action, globetrotting spies, and perfectly paced suspense, then you'll love this spy series from a <i>USA Today</i> best seller. </p>"; 
